### Ingest a note into the selected graph
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/aiService/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Rainbow Six Siege is a first-person shooter game.",
  "contextBoundaryId": "<context-boundary-id>",
  "actorId": "<actor-id>"
}

### Ask a question using the entire selected graph
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/aiService/prompt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "What games does this person like?",
  "contextBoundaryId": "<context-boundary-id>",
  "actorId": "<actor-id>"
}
